{"tid":114602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"都是食神頭銜惹的禍　謝霆鋒的肌肌一片血紅","createTime":"2017-02-10T01:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T07:21:47.000Z","uid":48800,"like":4,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17944f67747027b29af2994826367d0042aaed55","tid":114602,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"36歲謝霆鋒近年主持節目《12道鋒味》收視亮眼，更有「暖男食神」之稱，近年他將下廚的興趣結合工作，廚藝精進不少，不料他昨晚卻曬出慘烈的刮痧照，表示醫生已經警告他「不能再長期在廚房了」。<br />\n謝霆鋒昨晚秀出結實的上半身，只見刮痧痕遍及右手臂及右胸，令人觸目驚心，他表示：「醫生說不能再長期在廚房了，但是如果要在短時間內學會煮好任何東西，可能這就是代價了？」透露自己追逐夢想的決心。<br />\n粉絲看到照片嚇了一跳「原來是刮痧」、「峰哥看來最近身體不太好」；也有粉絲要他快回歸歌手本業「還是乖乖回去唱歌吧」、「說好的演唱會呢？等你呀」。（陳明慧／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21r907a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21r907a.jpg&h=605de59f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170206/1049741/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170206%2F1049741%2F&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=294e1392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170206/1049741/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食神<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37647d505128bde351e99b23d53206467f3c0cce","tid":114602,"uid":37482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"他知道，哭是沒有用的"},{"pid":"77bfc60a3eb43fc7af05fa8fb8c168ee591146e7","tid":114602,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711003c5b928d225c75cbb09e815bc5820e7f8c6","tid":114602,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:03:35.000Z","msg":"他透露近年拍戲經常受傷，手、腳、腰部都有舊患，醫生吩咐如果再不小心照料身體，到他三十七歲時，便要人攙扶或用拐杖才能行路。霆鋒一臉痛楚地説：&ldquo;之前拍《無極》，手指要纏住鐵線大耍鐵扇，可能因為那樣搞到食指到現在都伸不直，已經試過用針灸放血都不行，西醫就説是骨膜炎呀！而右腳又受過傷，現在每行一步都會有啪啪聲響，每天起身要休息五分鐘先可以落地行路。不過最嚴重都是脊椎骨，每次做音樂會太久都會覺得痛，看了幾百次醫生都沒有效。醫生説如果再是那樣，到我三十七歲就要人扶先行到路。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/news.xinhuanet.com/audio/2005-06/21/content_3113432.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.xinhuanet.com%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fnews.xinhuanet.com%2Faudio%2F2005-06%2F21%2Fcontent_3113432.htm&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7b07dec9\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/news.xinhuanet.com/audio/2005-06/21/content_3113432.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n癱未呀屌狄波拉"},{"pid":"ca2b342be39eb00d311f72eba7d2ce6f4f2a671b","tid":114602,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"咁D廚房佬係咪全部要坐輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84c95793d5c3eeccd73b4350dedee674a5dc803","tid":114602,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<br />\n做得個一陣就咁樣"},{"pid":"97779e4264fc74839ca64aab1ee7c700ef87ebad","tid":114602,"uid":35931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:14:03.000Z","msg":"我來刮！"},{"pid":"a5da83bfcdf702c60ffa4787d649b65531c2254c","tid":114602,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n識撚煮野咩佢"},{"pid":"9379bfade4631015a7422e0b1489e154988758e5","tid":114602,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁D廚房佬係咪全部要坐輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明廚房佬成日蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785e2a983dbbb8f73d6081c754cc7c83a45c117e","tid":114602,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"