"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有病 但會戰勝病魔</blockquote><br />\n做好爸爸"},{"pid":"a20625c806d7afe518ecc2a2abb43f2a9098c468","tid":114602,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"屌，技術未到家，人地廚師一日十幾個鐘係廚房都無事"},{"pid":"fab334aa2ab206d472b82eae546868fbf9c9b683","tid":114602,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"又出埋啲飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b8524bb29454058f00aba085232f02077a5e38","tid":114602,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"644c935664484ac41092767e62637f3344e97026","tid":114602,"uid":15063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢是咪真係當左自己食神"},{"pid":"465158c6f7ccafc6a65e5922e530a887e193181a","tid":114602,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人post返哭是沒有用"},{"pid":"3bd7097d0562f99576746fd0146be521f2effc01","tid":114602,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"46ab5ff20de995662bd78dd5a809c4cae0e82ae5","tid":114602,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"謝賢不停同人講佢仲有排玩<br />\n謝霆鋒就不停同人講佢無幾多日子玩"},{"pid":"9c51edd8f0f4628c79e3af036012a90d0510e8fd","tid":114602,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我來刮！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1da3647d5a463e5f6c45857c2d252945ab55d37","tid":114602,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3d/L5CBNdo.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140121134443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3d%2FL5CBNdo.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140121134443&h=047f6d56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5fabd7a2e6979ce5d97580fd37450b2d60b3963","tid":114602,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」<br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒為父還債，所以17歲出道，開始了自己的演藝生涯。霆鋒拍第一部片子《古惑仔》系列電影時，他和300多人打打殺殺，因為太過入戲，他不小心踢到了廢鋼鐵，腳立即受傷，血如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n導演立刻喊停，要送他去醫院。他知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「星途」也許從此就斷了。於是，17歲的他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著腳，穿上鞋子繼續拍攝。換了四個膠袋，倒出四袋血，戲拍完時，他幾乎暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。在給他縫針之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給他縫針時，謝霆鋒就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一針一針地縫著。一個17歲的少年，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。他知道，哭是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n最後一針，霆鋒對醫生說：「我來刮！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，他也只有四天的生命了，所以，他願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，他要給自己縫一針。<br />\n<br />\n從給自己縫針那一天開始，他知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，他一直努力，不停地得獎，終於成為第三十屆香港金像獎的影帝。"},{"pid":"97a08ad3a23f932fd5040f0767ab26336cadcf99","tid":114602,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3d/L5CBNdo.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140121134443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3d%2FL5CBNdo.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140121134443&h=047f6d56&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a82993ef581c9a5593efa1bd684d3c0d4eba11","tid":114602,"uid":6372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3d/L5CBNdo.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140121134443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3d%2FL5CBNdo.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140121134443&h=047f6d56&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf16aaf8183cf6ee36ab2d5cad467b6512c31eb","tid":114602,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"太多笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f163a90f334793207ba662ac9db3934923487e","tid":114602,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/71/Mkfung.gif/revision/latest?cb=20140121134332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.li